                <h2 class="text-dark">Features</h2>
                <ul class="text-dark">
                    <li>True multiplayer</li>
                    <li>Chat rooms and matchmaking capabilities</li>
                    <li>Comments on player statistics</li>
                    <li>Alerts when losing</li>
